The **Plagiarism Detector System** is built using the **Qt framework** and **C++ standard libraries**. 

## Project Goal

The primary objective of this project is to demonstrate our understanding of **data structures** and **algorithms**.

## Key Features

- Compares similarities between different text documents.
- Reads files in `.txt` format.
- Tokenizes words for analysis.
- Uses various algorithms for similarity comparison.

This project highlights our ability to apply computational techniques to practical problems.
